<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉nạ kmạnjẗ bạ̉wtạr wmfạtyḥ wbạsbḥ yswʿ ạlmsyḥ
 hllwyạ bạfrḥ lmạ ạ̉sbḥ yswʿ
 hllwyạ bạfrḥ wạ̉htf lh kmạnjẗ ạ̉ʿzf lh kmạnjẗ
 2- ạ̉nạ jytạr wʿndy st ạ̉wtạr wbạsbḥ bkwrdạt ktạr
 hllwyạ bạfrḥ lmạ ạ̉sbḥ yswʿ
 hllwyạ bạfrḥ wạ̉ʿzf lh ʿ ạljytạr
 3- ạ̉nạ ạ̉kwrdywn bmnfạkẖ wzrạyr btsbyḥy ạ̹blys ḥạyr
 hllwyạ bạfrḥ lmạ ạ̉sbḥ yswʿ
 hllwyạ bạfrḥ wạ̉ʿzf lh ạ̉kwrdywn
 4- ạ̉nạ sạksfwn ly ṭmwnạt ạ̉ʿzf lh ạ̉ḥly̱ ạltrnymạt
 hllwyạ bạfrḥ lmạ ạ̉sbḥ yswʿ
 hllwyạ bạfrḥ wạ̉ʿzf lh sạksfwn</lyrics>
<title>hllwyạ bạfrḥ</title>
</song>